snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard Defamation Case - An Defamation Attorney's Perspective
snippet.description:
Defamation Lawyer Raees Mohamed and Andrew Rossow discuss Johnny Depp's defamation lawsuit against Amber Heard on "What's The Legal Podcast". The two attorneys give their opinion on the judge's ruling in the lawsuit against The Sun Newspaper and more. 

To learn more about the lawsuits, check out our blog... https://rmwarnerlaw.com/2019/06/12/johnny-depps-50-million-defamation-lawsuit-against-amber-heard/
